## 6. System Model

VentraPOS is a **multi-tenant SaaS**.

### Multi-tenant means:
- many businesses use the same platform
- each business is isolated from every other business
- each business has its own stores, branches, staff, products, sales, expenses, customers, settings, and reports

### High-level hierarchy
```text
Platform
└── Business Account (Tenant)
    ├── Business Profile
    ├── Branches
    │   ├── Staff
    │   ├── Products / Inventory
    │   ├── POS Terminals / Sessions
    │   ├── Sales
    │   ├── Expenses
    │   └── Reports
    ├── Customers
    ├── Finance Settings
    ├── Permissions / Roles
    ├── Audit Logs
    └── Subscription / Billing
```

