## 7. Primary User Roles

## 7.1 Business Owner / Super Admin
Full control of the business.

Can:
- manage the business account
- create and edit branches
- view all reports
- add staff
- assign roles
- manage products
- view finances
- configure settings
- manage subscription

## 7.2 Branch Manager
Operates one branch or a subset of branches.

Can:
- view branch activity
- manage branch stock
- monitor staff
- view branch reports
- approve some actions depending on permissions

## 7.3 Cashier
Handles front-of-house sales.

Can:
- access POS
- process sales
- print or send receipts
- view assigned transaction history
- process refunds only if allowed

## 7.4 Stock Officer
Handles inventory operations.

Can:
- add stock
- adjust stock
- transfer stock
- track low stock
- mark damaged or expired items

## 7.5 Finance Officer / Accountant
Handles expenses and finance visibility.

Can:
- create and review expenses
- access finance summaries
- export records
- monitor revenue and cost trends

## 7.6 Platform Super Admin
Internal VentraPOS administrative role.

Can:
- manage tenants
- manage support workflows
- see platform health
- manage subscriptions
- handle incidents
- manage feature flags

