## 8. Primary Business Use Case

## Example business
**FreshMart Mini Supermarket**

### Business profile
- one small supermarket
- one main branch initially
- owner
- one cashier
- one manager
- one stock officer
- products such as drinks, rice, canned goods, milk, toiletries, bread, snacks

### What FreshMart needs
- create store profile
