## 14.14 Audit and Security Behavior

### Audit log targets
- stock adjustments
- product edits
- permission changes
- expense edits
- refunds
- price overrides
- login events
- suspicious actions

### Why this matters
Businesses can lose trust instantly if they cannot answer:
- who changed this
- when was this changed
- why did stock go missing
- who refunded this sale
- who altered the price

