## 20. Risks

## 20.1 Trust risk
If totals, stock, or reports are wrong, businesses lose trust immediately.

## 20.2 Security risk
If permissions are weak or data leaks across tenants, the platform fails at a foundational level.

## 20.3 UX risk
If onboarding is confusing, users do not become active.

## 20.4 POS speed risk
If checkout is slow, businesses stop using it.

## 20.5 Inventory risk
If stock logic is inconsistent, the product becomes dangerous for real operations.

