## 21. What VentraPOS Is Not

VentraPOS is **not**:
- only a POS screen
- only an accounting tool
- only an inventory tool
- a custom one-off build for one business
- a generic admin dashboard template

VentraPOS **is**:
- a structured multi-tenant SaaS
- a business operating system for SMEs
- an operational and financial visibility layer
- a product that helps businesses move from manual operations to digital control

